Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just about done myself.\NWhat's cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Special "beef with bell peppers."\NQing-jiao-rou-si.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Asimov Solensan.\NThis is our next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a high-end of the syndicate\Nthat deals all around the asteroids.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,About this Qing-jiao-rou-si...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy's name is Asimov Solensan.\NWeren't you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You DON'T call a meatless\N"beef with bell peppers"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,..."beef with bell peppers"...do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You do when you're broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the 1 million woolongs\Nwe got as bounty from that last guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The repair bill for\Nthe plane you wrecked...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the repair bill\Nfor the shop you trashed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the medical bill\Nof the cop you injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,KILLED ALL THE DOUGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days ago, there was a shootout\Nbetween his group and an enemy syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed his own men and took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They say he's hiding\Nwith his woman in Tijuana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a place for nobodies to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite being a nobody,\Nhe's worth 2.5 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tijuana... The beef there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...is REALLY tasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:40.16,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Attention, please.{\i0}\N{\i1}We will soon arrive at the gate. "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:42.63,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"We look forward to serving you again."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:59.28,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please line up single file at{\i0}\N{\i1}the tollbooth after clearing the gate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:04.08,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please pass by after switching{\i0}\N{\i1}the credit sensors to debit mode.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head over after\Nhitting the cops for clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll try seeing old man Bull.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you trust that old guy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an easygoing song.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,THIEF!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This again? Goddamn sonofabitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're totally ripping me off,\Nbut do ya realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...the reason you can\Nlive here is because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...I dug that gate with\Nall my might, ya hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This again.\NYou always say that when you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We all dug the gate together, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That we did.\NWe dug like there was no tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamn idiot sonofabitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll have a Bloody Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I got vodka, but unfortunately\NI'm out of tomato juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's ONE CAN\Nin the back room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Top-notch "RED-EYE."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd know, as a buyer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be..."BLOODY-EYE"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Prove to me that it's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep those eyes open!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is dandy,\Nbut you got anything to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The red-eyed coyote will appear\Nat the north end of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A red-eyed coyote, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You, "Swimming Bird."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall meet a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall be targeted\Nby that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then... death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Again. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Again"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already died once.\NGot killed by a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You take women too lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,May he be blessed by Wakantanka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Presidente?\NI'll have a glass on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. Asimov sure lost his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No shit. We gotta do something\Nbefore the cops start moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya wanna leave it up to the cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He IS using those eye drops.\NThere's no way we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tellin' ya, we got nothin' if\Nwe don't get that "BLOODY-EYE" back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give me the specifics?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to leave the water running.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it'll clog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...l'f soffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew! I don't want that anymore!\NYou can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lukfy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Felt like my stomach was\Ngoing to be glued to my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an old model.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been with me for over ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've gotten\Na lot of use out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I travel around a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually a wandering performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell if you're\Nfor real or just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people say that about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Been to Mars yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They have everything there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike here, Mars has lots\Nof people, lots of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They must live happily there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm sure we'll be happy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You planning on escaping to Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:14:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Running away...\Nbut how far can you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,An old-fashioned cowboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A bounty hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good call.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to catch us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your buddy seems to be pretty ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't deal with weakened nobodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU are the nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Asimov! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Adios, cowboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:15:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I coulda killed him in one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're tired.\NIf you do this anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He was young and attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting so long for\Nyou to come pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can finally escape the\Nlow life I've had here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can finally live happily on Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A nap. How peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a good dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can see the rest of\Nthat dream on the Bebop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving up on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When Asimov left his syndicate,\Nhe snuck something out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:16:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The top-end stuff of all the illegal\Neye drops that the syndicate makes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He took off with all of the drops,\Nso the group is in a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They wanna catch him,\Nbut all they get back are corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Asimov is using it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The eye drops known as "BLOODY-EYE."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're planning on going to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, they'll sell THIS off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I grabbed it from his breast pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You... met him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He got you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The red-eyed coyote will supposedly\Nappear at the north end of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This again? Goddamn sonofabitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're totally rippin' me off, but do\Nya realize the reason you can eat well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...around here is because I cultivated\Nthe land with my buddies, ya hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and that's us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That we did...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We planted seeds like\Nthere was no tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You were always planting "seeds"\Nof a different kind, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You have any Bloody Marys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I only got beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got tomato juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,300,000 woolongs.\NI got 50 packs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,15 million woolongs, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry. I'll find others\Nif you don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookin' for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know what YOU are worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:17:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 2.5 million woolongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a cheap guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when are you a buyer?\NDid you give up on bounty hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No thrill in cheap bounties.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you do better as a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You trust your eyes too much!\NYou're not a chameleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see everywhere all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That way! That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,IDIOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doomed if these break!\NBe more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Asimov.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Doing any more is insane!\NDon't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't run anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Adios...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spike, it's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Special "beef with bell peppers."
