Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.31,0:23:57.19,Bebop ED Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,700)}...ichido kiri de owaru nara...\N{\c&H37AB38&\3c&H37AB38&}...if it ends after the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.57,0:24:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, and so this program\Nis finally under way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.27,0:24:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Next week, we're completely changing\Ngears to show an anime for all ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.61,0:24:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it that kind of a story?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.14,0:24:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cheerful animals wreak havoc all over!\N- WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.34,0:24:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dr. Doolittle WON'T\Nbe making an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,From little kids to the elderly,\Nif you love animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.31,0:24:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on now, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.95,0:24:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone gather around\Nand watch the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.72,0:24:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right to\Nsay stuff like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.75,0:24:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not responsible for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.02,0:24:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is one favor\Nto ask right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.62,0:24:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good little kids should sit far\Nfrom the TV when watching the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.82,0:24:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.63,0:24:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back about a kilometer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.66,0:24:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's TOO far.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.99,0:24:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,800 meters then?

